window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Jay has gotten his cluster to come together.</b></p> <p>But new challenges always appear. Most frustrating is an old crush from Earth joins them and throws questions into all of Jay's relationships. One truth remains. Their only hope is to grow stronger. To do that, they have to descend deeper into the dungeon. At the same time, Jay has to decide how he feels about the women in his life. </p> <p><i>This book features unconventional relationships and some sexual content. It is intended for mature listeners. </i></p>"; 
